{"tid":175321,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"暴跌股有路捉，仲有咩好驚呀","createTime":"2017-03-27T12:14:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T00:27:13.000Z","uid":80270,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1fc0f8af6d31df90773918b6ebd51a5105da28db","tid":175321,"uid":80270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T12:14:39.000Z","msg":"【通告尋寶】<br />\n<br />\n上星期五輝山（6863）中午前突然急跌8成半，小編真係戥買左既朋友心痛。咁究竟，有無辦法係暴跌前搵出先兆呢？<br />\n<br />\n小編睇返最近一兩年暴跌股，包括恆發洋參（911，已改名為前海健康），樂亞控股（8195），漢能（566），同今次既輝山，發現原來個暴跌原因都關乎有控股股東抵押股份，抵押左既股票，無事就好地地，遇上波動補唔切倉，命運就好似佢地咁係咁先喇。<br />\n<br />\n比多個貼士大家，抵押左股票既公司，好多時都鍾意出自願性通告，話比人知控股股東增持架，點解，哈哈，自己諗下喇。<br />\n<br />\n所以，即刻睇清楚自己買左既股票，有無同樣情況喇👑<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/investeasywin/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Finvesteasywin%2F&d=dTdn096UhK%2BcydR5vLM298PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=84ea5ae9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/investeasywin/</a>"},{"pid":"b749475089a52a300a362a2b737b6ab67730c0d9","tid":175321,"uid":68821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T12:16:07.000Z","msg":"又宣傳fb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"387dd333f4afd7d3edd59755ce777f17b5589802","tid":175321,"uid":80270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T12:25:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又宣傳fb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又比你發現"},{"pid":"3551bce1c84b460eede81a9e7a41d9f1e0b1ac9a","tid":175321,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T21:31:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0df937c205c1b6270085eeb5410e01a490befe1c","tid":175321,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T21:31:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a3b27790a984d766571d66aa12d3df70ce53e5cf","tid":175321,"uid":91753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T00:00:59.000Z","